{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This-- we were treated like vermin, and we were-- became to think like that, because there was no hope.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was no-- nobody to protect you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Nobody to-- you could go to for any justice or any fairness or any reprieve.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You were just there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And anybody could do-- I'm talking before I was in Germany-- anybody could do with you whatever you wanted to.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this is a terrible feeling of insecurity, which remains with you all the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because you know how quickly all this can be destroyed or disturbed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it left an indelible mark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think all we survivors are damaged [BACKGROUND NOISE] beyond repair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But at that stage, in-- in-- in-- in Germany, when I felt that Germany's beginning to lose, I was hoping, you know, that for the liberation, I was looking forward to this moment of liberating and going back to Poland and finding the family who are somewhere, you know, in different ways, perhaps survived.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But my liberation was another nightmare, because I was liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the Russians have never taken any account, whether you were Jewish, or Russian, or Polish, or German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were raping and loitering all throughout.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it was another nightmarish experience, which I personally took very badly, because being liberated-- I took it as a punishment that I survived, that I deserved that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS] [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't know whether you want to talk about it, but it was a nightmarish experience, because it happened after I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't survive-- a lot of people survived, and I justify them completely, you know, because of different methods-- living with somebody-- this wasn't it.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
